Thank y’all for vibing with me this evening! 
A time was had! 

We were able to collect so many school supplies and I know that these kids and families will be so appreciative of your kind gestures ! 

@s.k.e.m_foundation and the Nola Dame Brand thanks you a million times! 

Thank you @fuzionforceatl for welcoming me with open arms! I’ll be back

On Friday, The @s.k.e.m_foundation and The Nola Dame Brand hosted a Benefit Dance Class where the objective was to collect school supplies for children and families in need of school supplies for this upcoming Back to School season. With the help of you alls both physical and monetary donations, we were able to donate over $300 worth of school supplies to Temple Elementary! 👏🏽👏🏽 

Our acts of kindness did not go unnoticed! The teachers and students of Temple Elementary thanks you! 

We were able to help supply their Care Closet which houses any and all things that students may need such as:
Clothes 
Shoes
Feminine Products
School supplies
Backpacks 
Deodorant
Lotions 
And Soooo much more! 

Again thank you Temple Elementary for always making me apart of the Tiger family
